(25,	'Product',	4693,	'Drive Medical Silver Sport 2 Wheelchair with Detachable Desk Arms and Swing away Footrests',	'P',	'DRI-SSP2',	NULL,	'Drive Medical',	'Drive Medical Silver Sport 2 Wheelchair with Detachable Desk Arms and Swing away Footrests',	'Right',	'<h2>Drive Medical Silver Sport 2 Wheelchair</h2> <p><span class=\"Heading2Char\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Are y</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ou worried about missing out on your favorite sports due to an injury? Looking to slip in a little bit of extra practice? Whether you have a physical disability or you&rsquo;re in the midst of recovering from an injury, you can still easily practice and play at your own leisure. A wheelchair made for sports is made to get you over indoor courts with ease without assistance. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /> <br /> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">If you&rsquo;re ready to take on new challenges and keep playing the games you love, you may consider a sports edition wheelchair from Drive Medical. Currently, Drive is a leading Canadian brand with on-point mobility solutions, allowing you to enjoy the games you love.</span></p> <p>The <a title=\"Drive Medical\" href=\"https://www.halohealthcare.com/brands/Drive-Medical.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Drive Medical</strong></a> Silver Sport 2 Wheelchair is perfect for the elderly or disabled individuals with limited mobility as it allows them the freedom of independence. The wheelchair comes in an attractive style that is powder coated with a silver vein finish. It is easy to maintain and has a steel frame, which makes the wheelchair durable even in times of wear and tear.</p> <h2>Silver Sport 2 - Durable and Lightweight</h2> <p>The Drive Medical Silver Sport 2 Wheelchair has urethane tires that are mounted on composite wheels. This allows the user to ride smoothly over most surfaces without any fear of the tires slipping. The wheelchair also has embossed, nylon upholstery that is easy to clean. It is durable and lightweight, whic